---
title: Cannellini Bean & Veggie Enchiladas with Cheddar & Garlic Aioli
description: Who said you can’t have delicious veggie-based enchiladas? Okay, probably no one but if they ever do this dish is here to prove them
wrong! Buttery and saucy cannellini beans are cooked to perfection in our enchilada sauce alongside spiced veggies. Wrap it up in the
tortillas, add a fresh salsa and lots of cheese and there you have it, living, great smelling proof of the best veggie enchiladas.
